  & = (\mathbf{U}^{H} \mathbf{A} \mathbf{U})^{H} (\mathbf{U}^{H} \mathbf{A} \mathbf{U})
  \\
  & = \mathbf{U} \mathbf{A}^{H} \mathbf{U}^{H} \mathbf{U}^{H} \mathbf{A} \mathbf{U}
  \\
  & = \mathbf{U}^{H} \mathbf{A}^{H} \mathbf{U} \mathbf{U}^{H} \mathbf{A} \mathbf{U}
